[
    {
        "Key": "page1.1",
        "Speaker": "？？？",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "亲爱的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.2",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "耳边传来了一阵熟悉的声音。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.3",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但是我环顾四周，却没有发现有人的踪迹。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.4",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那答案只有一个了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.5",
        "Speaker": "H主角",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "出来吧，凯茜娅。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.6",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我手朝着前方的空气一挥，凯茜娅果不其然出现在我面前。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.7",
        "Speaker": "H主角",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "信息态可逃不过我的眼睛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.8",
        "Speaker": "H凯茜娅",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我当然知道，不过就是想来一点小小的情趣。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.9",
        "Speaker": "H主角",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你用信息态搞得情趣可不少了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.10",
        "Speaker": "H凯茜娅",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "比如半夜到你的房间，又或者突然出现在你放好热水的浴室里？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.11",
        "Speaker": "H主角",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这要都说出来，一时半会可就说不完了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.12",
        "Speaker": "H凯茜娅",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯哼，有时候我也在想，既然亲爱的对泰坦物质这么敏锐。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.13",
        "Speaker": "H凯茜娅",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那我平常做的这些应该不会没有预知吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.14",
        "Speaker": "H主角",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "当然有，也正如你说，我也保持一点情趣感。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.15",
        "Speaker": "H凯茜娅",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "既然如此的话……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.16",
        "Speaker": "H凯茜娅",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "今晚上，我可也要准时出现在你的床前了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.17",
        "Speaker": "H凯茜娅",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "记得做好准备，亲爱的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.18",
        "Speaker": "H主角",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "早就准备好了，或者说？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.19",
        "Speaker": "H主角",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不如就现在。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.20",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "话音未落，我握住了凯茜娅的手。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.21",
        "Speaker": "H主角",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这样你变成信息态也走不掉了哦。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.22",
        "Speaker": "H凯茜娅",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "亲爱的，我可没说要走。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.23",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "凯茜娅借着我手的力，率先吻了上来。",
        "disable": 0
    }
]